Package: MadIsland
Type: Package
Title: Package to hold all the scripts to reproduce paper on colonisation and 
    divesification history of Madagascar's tetrapods
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person(given = "Joshua W.",
           family = "Lambert",
           email = "j.w.l.lambert@rug.nl",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5218-3046"))
Maintainer: Joshua W. Lambert <j.w.l.lambert@rug.nl>
Description: Reproduce all analyses and plots from the paper on the colonisation
    and diversification history of Madagascar's tetrapods. Note that this package
    is tailored to use the Hábrók High Performance Computing Cluster (HPCC) 
    <https://wiki.hpc.rug.nl/habrok/start> therefore rerunning certain analyses
    sequentially on a desktop/laptop will be time consuming.
License: GPL (>= 3)
